   840	
   841	Unrelated to signals, delivered on the same channel because it is the same
   842	kind of lifecycle fact: `onBeforeMutation(container)` /
   843	`onAfterMutation(container)` bracket exactly the window in which React
   844	mutates the host tree during a commit, so an application `MutationObserver`
   845	can disconnect around React's own writes and observe everything else. The
   846	signals library itself never references MutationObserver.
